               <msContents>
                  <summary>Deluxe Psalter, ዳዊት፡. Psalm 1 (f. i r, top); Record of vow of person from whom a demon has been exorcised (f. i r, bottom); List of the feast days of the Saints and Apostles (ff. i v); Asmat Prayer against wild animals (ff. i v - ii r) (f. ii v, in blue ink);  Psalter, ዳዊት፡ (f<locus target="#1r"/>-122r); Image of the Praises of Mary, መልክአ፡ ውዳሴ፡, incipit: ፈቀደ: እግዚእ: ለአዳም: ያግዕዞ: (Chaîne, Répertoire 398, MG59 701ff) (f<locus target="#122r"/>-128r); Image of the Gate of Light, መልክዐ፡ አንቀጸ፡ ብርሃን፡, incipit, ቅድስት: ወብፅዕት: በልሳነ: ኵሉ: ዘነፍስ: (Chaîne, Répertoire 241, MG59 728ff.) (f<locus target="#128r"/>-129v); Hymn to Mary, “For the Love of the Father, the Son, and the Holy Spirit, Our Father,” incipit, በእንተ: ፍቅረ: አብ: ወወልድ: ወመንፈስ: ቅዱስ: አቡነ: (no Chaîne, Répertoire number) (f<locus target="#129v"/>-131r); List of the Feast Days (<locus target="#131r"/>); Asmat prayer for drowning demons, ጸሎት: በእንተ: መስጥመ: አጋንንት:, incipit, በስመ: አብ: በል::ጸሎት: በእንተ: መስጥም: ባሪያ: ወሌጌዎን: መስጥም: ይዘኩም:...(f<locus target="#131v"/>-132v); List of the Feast Days (<locus target="#132v"/>); Prayer on the Hebrew Alphabet, incipit, በስመ: አብ: ወወልድ... አሌፍ: ርድአኒ: በየማንከ: ልዕልት: ወበመዝራእትከ: ጽንእት:.. (f<locus target="#133r"/>-134r); Asmat Prayer, “I Beseech You Lest I die Early,” ተማኅጸንኩ: ከመ: ኢይሙት: ዘእንበለ: ጊዜየ, incipit, በስመ: አብ: ወወልድ:...ተማኅፀንኩ: አንሰ: ከመ: ኢይሙት: ዘእንበለ: ጊዜየ:... (f<locus target="#134rv"/>); Deluxe Psalter from Government scriptorium (?).</summary>
